 Finally, the game will have regular seasons, they have time constraints and different conditions. 

00:03:12.033 --> 00:03:16.300
 In each season, each front will host a variety of game activities. 

00:03:16.400 --> 00:03:19.533
 Winning in the event allows players to get a variety of rewards. 

